query:
INSERT INTO deal_labels (deal_id, piece_cid, label_raw, payload_cid)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
            ON CONFLICT (deal_id) DO UPDATE SET
                piece_cid = EXCLUDED.piece_cid,
                label_raw = EXCLUDED.label_raw,
                payload_cid = EXCLUDED.payload_cid,
                fetched_at = NOW()
